description: Beefy Julian Torres and Alex Tikas are in the eye of the corona, as they say, and are happy to be together. You could just play board games but... they have a feeling you're not here for monopoly. In fact, they're already hard just thinking about showing off exactly how they've been spending their time together. Besides, just because they can't touch you, doesn't mean you can't touch yourself!
title: Furry Beefy Fuckers
